name: Chemical Thermodynamics and Elementary Kinetics
description: The concept of chemical potential; phase equilibria; solutions; chemical equilibria (including electrochemical applications); elementary reactions; multi-step and coupled reactions (with biochemical applications); elementary collision theory and transition state theory.
prerequisites: [CHMA10H3 and CHMA11H3] and MATA30H3 and [MATA35H3 or MATA36H3] and PHYA10H3
